# Components

## Cards
- Always use abp-card
- Separate sections clearly

## Buttons
- Primary = main action
- Secondary = cancel
- Danger = delete

## Table
- Hoverable rows
- Striped rows
- Action column on right

## Badge
- Published: green
- Draft: gray
- Pending: orange